Five local authorities have come together to establish a combined authority for the Tees Valley area.

They are:

Darlington;

Hartlepool;

Middlesbrough;

Redcar & Cleveland;

Stockton-on-Tees.

This is the Tees Valley Combined Authority.

The combined authority will improve economic prosperity in the Tees Valley.

Building on the already recognised unity and our ability to work together.
